    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164460/extras/e4816e81e1c0b0e31c0ccd5fb40cae54.avif?t=1767214014\" width=616 height=314 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-You have been trapped in a warp cube. Every faction of the Cube Federation is out to get you. You are on your own, but you were trapped for a reason. Make them pay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Use your main weapons, a charge shot, incredible speed, power crystals dropped occasionally by defeated cubes, and even the warp cube itself to fight the Cube Federation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight various cubes, big cubes, and boss &quot;<i>cubes</i>&quot; to draw out the most powerful ship in the Federation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-After beating the biggest enemy of them all, the real game can begin, test your skill in the endless mode and fight tooth and nail to achieve the highest score possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164460/extras/de9452528db9155001215517c41f5ece.poster.avif?t=1767214014\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164460/extras/de9452528db9155001215517c41f5ece.webm?t=1767214014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164460/extras/de9452528db9155001215517c41f5ece.mp4?t=1767214014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
